# BidGuard: API Design (Ultra-MVP)

## Overview

REST API з мінімальним набором endpoints для MVP.

- Base URL: `http://localhost:4000/api`
- Production: `https://api.bidguard.app/api`

---

## Authentication

### Headers

```
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

### Token Lifecycle

- Access Token: JWT, 1 година
- Refresh Token: JWT, 7 днів, httpOnly cookie (`bid_refresh`)

---

## Response Format

### Success

```json
{
  "data": { ... }
}
```

### Error

```json
{
    "error": {
        "code": "ERROR_CODE",
        "message": "Human readable message"
    }
}
```

### Error Codes

| Code                   | HTTP | Description              |
| ---------------------- | ---- | ------------------------ |
| `UNAUTHORIZED`         | 401  | Missing or invalid token |
| `INSUFFICIENT_CREDITS` | 402  | No credits available     |
| `NOT_FOUND`            | 404  | Resource not found       |
| `VALIDATION_ERROR`     | 400  | Invalid request          |
| `INTERNAL_ERROR`       | 500  | Server error             |

---

## Endpoints

### Auth

#### GET /auth/google

Redirect to Google OAuth consent screen. Passport automatically redirects — no request body.

**Response:** 302 Redirect to Google

---

#### GET /auth/google/callback

Google OAuth callback. Passport processes the code, creates/finds user, sets refresh cookie.

**Response:** 302 Redirect to `{WEB_URL}/auth/callback`

- Sets `bid_refresh` httpOnly cookie (7 days)

---

#### POST /auth/magic-link/send

Send magic link to email.

**Request:**

```json
{
    "email": "user@example.com"
}
```

**Response (200):**

```json
{
    "data": {
        "message": "Magic link sent to email"
    }
}
```

---

#### POST /auth/magic-link/verify

Verify magic link token.

**Request:**

```json
{
    "token": "magic_token_from_email"
}
```

**Response (200):**

```json
{
  "data": {
    "user": { ... },
    "accessToken": "eyJ..."
  }
}
```

- Sets `bid_refresh` httpOnly cookie (7 days)

---

#### POST /auth/refresh

Refresh access token.

**Request:** Cookie `bid_refresh` required

**Response (200):**

```json
{
    "data": {
        "accessToken": "new_access_token"
    }
}
```

---

#### POST /auth/logout

Logout and clear cookies.

**Response (200):**

```json
{
    "data": {
        "message": "Logged out"
    }
}
```

