# BidGuard

**Your Digital Auto Expert for US Auction Purchases**

BidGuard is an AI-powered platform that analyzes vehicle photos from US auto auctions (Copart, IAAI) to detect hidden defects and provide instant risk assessments. We help buyers avoid costly mistakes by identifying issues that are often invisible to the untrained eye.

## Key Features

- **Instant Analysis** - Get comprehensive vehicle reports in 30 seconds, 24/7
- **Hidden Defect Detection** - AI-powered visual analysis catches masked damage, repainted areas, and deployed airbags
- **Risk Assessment** - Clear verdicts with red flags, repair cost estimates, and buy/skip recommendations
- **Cost-Effective** - Fraction of the cost of traditional expert consultations ($50-100)

---

## Project Structure

```
bidguard/
├── apps/                       # Main applications
│   ├── web/                    # Next.js 16 frontend (App Router, React 19)
│   └── api/                    # NestJS 11 backend (MongoDB/Mongoose)
│
├── packages/                   # Shared packages
│   └── types/                  # @bidguard/types - shared TypeScript types
│
├── docs/                       # Documentation
│   └── BUSINESS_CONCEPT.md     # Business concept and strategy
