## Auth Flow (OAuth + Magic Link)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        AUTH FLOW                                 │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                  │
│  Option 1: Google OAuth                                          │
│  ───────────────────────                                         │
│  1. User clicks "Sign in with Google"                            │
│  2. Redirect to Google consent screen                            │
│  3. Google redirects back with auth code                         │
│  4. Backend exchanges code for user info                         │
│  5. Create/update user in MongoDB                                │
│  6. Generate JWT tokens                                          │
│  7. Redirect to /check with tokens                               │
│                                                                  │
│  Option 2: Magic Link                                            │
│  ────────────────────────                                        │
│  1. User enters email                                            │
│  2. Backend generates magic token (store in Redis, TTL 15min)    │
│  3. Send email with magic link                                   │
│  4. User clicks link                                             │
│  5. Backend verifies token from Redis                            │
│  6. Create/update user in MongoDB                                │
│  7. Generate JWT tokens                                          │
│  8. Redirect to /check with tokens                               │
│                                                                  │
│  Token Strategy:                                                 │
│  ─────────────────                                               │
│  - Access Token: JWT, 1 hour, in memory/localStorage             │
│  - Refresh Token: JWT, 7 days, httpOnly cookie                   │
│                                                                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

