## Report Processing Pipeline

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    REPORT PROCESSING                             │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                  │
│  1. [Controller] POST /reports                                   │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  2. [Service] Check user credits (balance > 0 OR !freeUsed)     │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  3. [Service] Create report (status: pending)                    │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  4. [Service] Deduct credit OR mark freeReportUsed = true       │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  5. [Storage] Generate presigned URLs for photo uploads          │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  6. [Client] Upload photos directly to R2                        │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  7. [Controller] POST /reports/:id/analyze                       │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  8. [Queue] Add job to BullMQ                                    │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  9. [Processor] Process job:                                     │
│         ├── Download photos from R2                              │
│         ├── For each photo: Call AI API (Gemini Flash)           │
│         ├── Parse AI response                                    │
│         ├── Aggregate issues                                     │
│         ├── Calculate verdict                                    │
│         └── Update report (status: completed)                    │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  10. [Client] Poll GET /reports/:id/status                       │
│         │                                                        │
│         ▼                                                        │
│  11. [UI] Show completed report                                  │
│                                                                  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

